en.Title: Quantum Algorithm Company Quanscient Secures €5.2 Million in Growth Funding
en.Summary: Quanscient, a company specializing in quantum algorithms, has successfully raised €5.2 million to support its growth initiatives.
en.Subject: Funding, Quantum Computing
